Class Dice

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Dice
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DemoDice

    public class Dice
extends Object
    This class can throw 'x' amount of dice with 'y' sides

    Random numbers are generated to simulate the amount/sides.
